text: Where did my kidney go, and skeleton?

parts.text:
*AHAHAHAHA!*  Mein patient! You ask of your kidney and skeleton?  *Wunderbar!*  Such excellent questions for a post-operative examination!  

Let me see… your kidney?  Ah, yes, zat was… *interesting*.  It was a bit… *small*, you see? Not nearly enough potential for my experiments. So, I replaced it with a slightly larger one! From a… *baboon*.  A very *robust* baboon.  You should feel a marked improvement in your… *renal output*.  

And your skeleton? *Ooooohohoho!* Now *that* was a project!  I found some… *minor* structural inefficiencies.  So I, uh… *rearranged* a few things. Added a couple of extra ribs for good measure! You know, for *structural integrity*. And perhaps a touch more… *elegance*?  It’s a masterpiece, I tell you!  A work of art!  A *functional* work of art!  Though I may have accidentally misplaced a few vertebrae… somewhere… *in the lab*. But don't worry, they're completely replaceable!  *AHAHAHAHA!*
